        <title>Area and Carbon Content of Sphagnum Peatlands in North America and Eurasia Since the Last Glacial Maximum</title>
        <onlink>http://daac.ornl.gov/metadata/bluangel_harvest/RGED/QC/basic/soils/sphagnum_peatlands_carbon.xml</onlink>
